name: Dar Open Network
public_notice:
Mines of Dalarnia (DAR) has been rebranded to Dar Open Network (D). They migrated from their old contract and old contract to new contract and new contract. For more information, please visit this post for more information and visit the old token page here.
According to two Goplus reports (1, 2), this is a proxy contract. The contract owner can make code changes to the token contract including but not limited to disabling sells, changing fees, minting, transferring tokens etc. Exercise caution.
